# API Key Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# .env.local is git-ignored and will never be committed.
#
# NOTE: This project is fully browser-based. API keys are entered directly
# in the tool UI at runtime — they are never stored on any server.
# This file is purely for documentation / local dev reference.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Google Gemini API Key (used by tools with AI transcript analysis)
# Get yours at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
